<item>
            <title>[LU-8503] Replay-single test-66b: @@@@@@ FAIL: Worst 6 should be worse than orig 6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8503</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The replay-single test_66b invokes lookup to initiate a RPC. Running this test successively causes the lookup to fetch inodes from cache without sending RPC. This results in test injection failing. Replacing lookup with touch resolves this issue.&lt;/p&gt;
